        <abstract> 
<p>Pleased JSBS has decided to work on <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>; sends plants. Does not know whether thermo-electric pile could detect temperature change when leaves close.</p> 
            <p>CD’s experiment with very weak hydrochloric acid repeated with success: the plants digest albumen more quickly.</p>
        </abstract>
